程序包 org.modelmapper.spi

接口 ValueWriter<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - destination type
    所有已知实现类:
    MapValueWriter, ProtobufValueWriter
    public interface ValueWriter<T>
    Writes values to a destination. Allows for integration with 3rd party libraries.
